description:
Video phal taka min hman tirtu Drew Pachuau (Inhouse) chungah thinlung takin lawmthu kan sawi e.

1.He lei ka dam chhungin
   Khawvel hlimna par tlan tur neilo in
   Chhuan tur neilo mah ila
   Nang ka nei che Lalpa

      Ka thawh chhuah theih loh rosum
      Ka phu loh malsawmna 
      In min vur si; Ava mak em Lalpa
      Ka tan i ui silo

2.Tunah chuan rethei in 
    Lenrual zingah hlimni awm lo mahse
    I kianga ka thlen hun chuan
    Hlim in ka leng tawh ang
  
 He lei ah zawng tap in
   Hrehawm tuar mah ila
   Ka Pa lalram ka thlen hun chuan
   Lawm avangin mittui a luang tawh ang.
